          "The chantry in Los Angeles has good foundations and has been built well between Dafne Pictor and Pedro Villalobos. Continue to grow and maintain the strength of the clan in the domain, whatever that takes."
        ],
        [
          "You have always been curious about not just the survival of the Tremere but the growth and the evolution of the Tremere in the Ascension War. Continue your research into that and see if there are secrets hidden elsewhere from others who may have had the same idea."
        ],
        [
          "There are rumors of renegade followers of Carna, attempting to create their own faction. Thus far, they've been nothing more than rebels, already marked for death by the clan. Squash their influence before it spreads."
        ],
